text.tspan: Oh Lord, for this I pray
Renew my mind, oh Lord, day by day dispense Your life;
Replace my will, oh Lord, with Your will that I would say
“Oh Lord, Amen,” always trusting You, following You.
Increase my love for You so that I would love You,
Return Your love with Yours, responding to Your call;
Reveal more of Yourself to me so I can see
Your divine economy, shine on me Your speaking.
